content_html: Kathmandu, Sept 15: President Ramchandra Paudel has extended best wishes for happiness, peace and prosperity to all Nepalis on the occasion of Jitiya Parva. In a message of greetings, President Paudel has expressed confidence that the unique festivals like Jitiya make contributions to maintain and promote social unit
